573
00:41:58,926 --> 00:42:02,423
Reci mi nešto o mojoj tetki.

574
00:42:04,799 --> 00:42:10,672
Imate li maramicu ili neki
odevni predmet,

575
00:42:10,779 --> 00:42:12,779
ili deo nakita koji mogu da
koristim?

576
00:42:12,834 --> 00:42:15,049
Moje bisere.

577
00:42:23,591 --> 00:42:26,020
Divni su.

578
00:42:32,427 --> 00:42:34,427
Da.

579
00:42:36,884 --> 00:42:40,648
